  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Mid- and low-lying rectal cancer (between 0 and 11 cm from the anal margin)

          -  Histology of adenocarcinoma

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Locally advanced disease (T4)

          -  Emergency surgery

          -  Rectal cancer over familial colic polyposis
      </textblock>
